headline: Down 42%, Can This Growth Stock Double a $1,000 Investment in 5 Years?
summary: Revenue for this powerful consumer brand only grew 6% in Q1, slower than the double-digit gains over the past few years.  Investors can appreciate management’s relentless focus on product innovation.  One growth stock is currently 42% off its peak.
